{"tid":918403,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【仍是盟友?】 馮檢基:沒有芥蒂 李卓人:不作回應","createTime":"2018-11-27T07:46:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-27T18:41:25.000Z","uid":37554,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"4b3816afcafb459bd519f8f3dce1ea7ca273801f","tid":918403,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T07:46:24.000Z","msg":"馮檢基:沒有芥蒂<br />\n李卓人:不作回應<br />\n<br />\n在立法會九龍西補選落敗的馮檢基與李卓人，早上出席在本台節目《千禧年代》時，被問到雙方日後是否仍是盟友。馮檢基說，與李卓人之間並無芥蒂，如果對方日後繼續爭取民主，一樣會是他的盟友。<br />\n<br />\n至於李卓人則說，無想過與馮檢基現時是甚麼關係，不會回應，他認為目前更重要是聆聽無出來投票及投票予其他候選人的選民聲音。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/RTHKVNEWS/videos/348388555719127/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FRTHKVNEWS%2Fvideos%2F348388555719127%2F&d=LFry4mU5MBWBgVoBxpk3xTCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=3abab523\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/RTHKVNEWS/videos/348388555719127/</a>"},{"pid":"10e1861256676aebd72e3a84b0fa9fd681d73604","tid":918403,"uid":22736,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T07:52:57.000Z","msg":"錢已袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c27bcc715e9f7b6823d9d770bd9823740976a4a7","tid":918403,"uid":203878,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T07:57:09.000Z","msg":"人哥做乜咁無風度呀。。。不過一個月冇左9萬8又難怪咁嬲嬲豬嘅。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"149ee7ae8a2c3f1e70264c78dbae9eabf6ecff34","tid":918403,"uid":15660,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T08:25:32.000Z","msg":"支持基哥<br />\n名正言順<br />\n報名參選自己紮根既選區合情合理<br />\n你李卓人走過黎做乜鳩呀"},{"pid":"8683d16900d56e9d96dc24b88f8b9e405c810cec","tid":918403,"uid":38982,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T08:27:19.000Z","msg":"李卓人正一小氣又無用既廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" c